{
  "stem": "21786.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what one could do for them was extremely limited.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had some material for pain, occasionally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was distributed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was even, when we brought enough supply, even injected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As far as the surgery which was done there, which I witnessed, was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] couple of times there was an emergency appendectomy performed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then there was performed a sterilization on one of the females.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm sure it was under the sterilization program, which was done by Mengele.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then, I have seen probatory kind of a lobotomy-- cut into the abdomen of a couple of twins, female twins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whether samples were taken, or whether it was observed or inspected by Mengele, himself, I cannot report.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were performed under ether, under ether.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think we had any local anesthetics-- no, ether, or chloroform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was present about on three, four occasions when abortions were done on prisoner women-- women, for to be pregnant was a certain death.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No pregnancy allowed, naturally, no possible showing of being pregnant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a kind of merciful act which had to be done very secretly, without the knowledge of the SS.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were three prisoner doctors who were very humane, and who I have never seen doing anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were about 16 or 20 nursing personnel, who probably, when they found out a corpse, so obviously they confiscated the bread or whatever supply there was, which was quite understandable.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can give you the name-- names of the doctors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Bardach, B-A-R-D-A-C-H, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Heller, H-E-L-L-E-R, and Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Winternitz, W-I-- W-I-N-T-E-R-N-I-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Two of them went with me then from Auschwitz to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Schwarzheide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one of them survived, Bardach survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
